== Channels ==

Here are a few Emacs-related Gitter channels. You will need a Github account to participate.

* https://gitter.im/clojure-emacs/
* https://gitter.im/syl20bnr/spacemacs
* https://gitter.im/magit/magit
* https://gitter.im/bbatsov/prelude
* https://gitter.im/ensime/ensime-emacs

[https://gitter.im/explore/tags/emacs Browse the "emacs" tag for more]


== Connecting to gitter ==
* there is a client for Emacs at https://github.com/xuchunyang/gitter.el 
* you can connect with [[ERC|your favourite IRC client]] by getting a token at http://irc.gitter.im/




